    "Name": "New Dawn ND-RRDS",
    "Details": "The ND-RRDS is a special mixed-technology variant built in 3102 to mark the formal partnership between Riley's Rangers and Clan Sea Fox, and at nearly 60 million C-Bills one of the most expensive 75-ton designs ever produced. A clan-made 300 XXL engine frees tonnage for a HAG/40 as the primary weapon alongside a Streak LRM 10 and a right arm loaded with a Large X-Pulse Laser and twin Medium X-Pulse Lasers. All ammunition is protected by CASE II.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>",
